Prepare coffee with shredded orange peel (if desired) and the water in a drip coffee maker or percolator according to manufacturer's directions. Pour coffee into a heatproof pitcher; stir in LACTAID(R) Reduced Fat Milk and sugar. Chill at least 3 hours before serving. To serve, fill 6 glasses with ice cubes; pour coffee mixture over ice. Garnish with orange peel strips, if desired.